# 3. (0.3*0.2+0.3*0.1+0.2*0.3+0.2*0.4) / sqrt((0.3^2+0.3^2+0.2^2+0.2^2) * (0.2^2+0.1^2+0.3^2+0.4^2)) = 0.823532105
